NUMBER 204
NAME Bazaar Northeast
MONSTER_GROUP 1
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Normally this is the drabbest corner of the whole bazaar. A stone building, entirely colorless, displays only the words "TARINTH'S ETERNITY, INC." engraved above the single door leading in. Work crews walk in and out of this area; their efforts focus on the apparent development of a new street to the north.
*DESCRIPTION_END
OUTDOOR_OTHER
FIXED_LIGHT
