NUMBER 250
NAME Main Street & Pleasant & Commerce
OUTDOOR_OTHER
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This hub intersection still shows signs of damage from the war. Main Street comes to an end, and Pleasant and Commerce both terminate or begin here, depending on how you look at it. Workers continue to mill about the area, hauling loads of rubble from sites to the west. Other pedestrians are split between banged up and nicked adventurers heading for the Physicians' Guild, and merchants and craftsmen delivering their work for sale at the bazaar.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT SW 275
EXIT E 251
EXIT S 249
EXIT W 2812
