NUMBER 2863
NAME Seti's Tomb
*DESCRIPTION_START
The utter darkness and musty air betray that you are very deep underground. Ancient pictoral writing adorns the crumbling walls, and tiny torches flicker with just enough light that you can spot an opening in the floor. The center of the floor is dominated by an elaborate sarcophagus.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
EXIT D 2862
ITEM 0 234 CLOSED
